==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Physicism
<hw>Phys"i*cism</hw> <pr>(f⟦icr⟧z"⟦icr⟧*s⟦icr⟧z'm)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos>
<def>The tendency of the mind toward, or its preoccupation with,
physical phenomena; materialism in philosophy and religion.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><q>Anthropomorphism grows into theology, while <qex>physicism</qex>
(if I may so call it) develops into science.</q>
<rj><qau>Huxley.</qau></rj>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Physicist</ent>⟦br⟧
